    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a great new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag! It\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready to hit the road with you today. I've taken great care of it, and it's got plenty of life left for all your adventures. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 31500.0,
