    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six. This unit retains its high-revving character with crisp throttle response via individual throttle bodies. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels via the M-variable differential lock. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and updated VANOS seals, ensuring structural rigidity and timing accuracy. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing factory-spec bushings and dampers for communicative feedback. While showing minor aesthetic patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014specifically rod bearing clearances and compression across all six cylinders\u2014are within optimal operating parameters. This is a mechanically sound example ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car for sale. Good condition. Mechanically sound. Clean interior. Regular maintenance performed. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 29500.0,
