    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous shine, though a keen eye might spot a few minor stone chips consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery remains supple with only light natural creasing on the driver's seat bolster, and it has been kept strictly smoke-free. Mechanically, this car has been fastidiously maintained with a documented service history. The engine purrs quietly at idle and provides smooth, responsive acceleration through every gear. We recently performed a full fluid flush and fitted a fresh set of tires to ensure the next owner enjoys a turn-key experience. From the crystal-clear premium sound system to the seamless operation of the power sunroof, every feature functions exactly as intended. It\u2019s a dependable, attractive ride that has many miles of adventure left to offer.",
      "price": 34500.0,
